 null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "O Allah! Send blessings on Muhammad and the Household of Muhammad, and hasten His (Imam Zamaan a.t.f.s.) advent, and destroy their enemies from both jinn and human beings, both the foremost and the later ones.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Ay Ma’bood! Rehmat naazil farma Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur unki Aal (a.s) par aur unke Zuhoor mein taajil (jaldi) farma aur halaak kar Muhammad (s.a.w.a) aur Aale Muhammad (a.s) ke dushmano ko, jinnato’n aur insaano se awwalin aur aakherin se.", "Urdu": "اے معبود!محمدؐ اور اس کی آل ؑپر رحمت فرما اوران کے ظہور میں تعجیل فرمااور محمدؐوآل محمدؐ کے دشمنوں کو ہلاک کرخواہ وہ جنّوں میں سے ہیں یاانسانوں میں سے اولین سے ہیں یا آخرین سے۔", "RArabic": "ALLAAHUMMA SALLE A’LAA MUHAMMADIW WA AALE MUHAMMADIN WA A’JJIL FARAJA-JUM, WA AHLIK A’DOOWA-HUM MENAL JINNE WAL INSE, MENAL AWWA-LEENA WAL AAKHE-REENA.", "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ صَلِّ عَلٰى مُحَمَّدٍ وَّاٰلِ مُحَمَّدٍ وَعَجِّلْ فَرَجَهُمْ، وَاَهْلِكْ عَدُوَّهُمْ مِنَ الْجِنِّ وَالْاِنْسِ، مِنَ الْاَوَّلِيْنَ وَالْاٰخِرِيْنَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "A